Turner Broadcasting System Inc's CNNsaid it reached an agreement with China Central Television toair its news programming in China.    It said China Central TV will use CNN reports during itsdaily newscasts on two channels, reaching an audience of about300 mln viewers.    The company said the agreement also gives CNN the right tosell advertising spots on China Central TV.    CNN also said it reached an agreement with Televerket KabelTV of Sweden to broadcast 24-hour news on its cable TV network.The program will reach an initial 118,000 viewers. Reuter&#3;